Key Match Events: David Brooks scored in the third minute
Neco Williams made it 2-0 in the 38th
Teemu Pukki scored Finland's goal in the 45th
Brennan Johnson restored the two-goal cushion in the 47th
Dan James scored the fourth goal in the 86th
Post-Match Reflections: Manager Rob Page said 'it could have been five or six'
Page added that Wales has come a long way and must continue to work hard
Page praised Dan James for his performance and goal
